caption:
Pre-Serum Steve x Reader

Understand - Gify July

“Don’t worry, she’ll understand.”  Bucky told Steve as he put his hand on his shoulder.
“Buck…  She told me she wanted to get married and have kids, and I just.  I need to be in this war, I need to help people.  I’m not sure she will understand.”  Steve’s head dropped, but Bucky’s head snapped up as he looked through the door behind Steve.
“Well she puts up with your late rear-end.”  You said from the doorway, having heard what they were talking about.  “Come on let’s talk about this.  Dinner’s ready, Bucky you staying?”  You asked smiling gently.

Summary:

Steve Rogers is about to begin the first day of his last year of high school and he’s all around pessimistic. Between being an easy target for bullies in school and Bucky having left for college, he’s anticipating a hell of a long year before he’s finally out.
